    • AppStartInfo

      public AppStartInfo​(int day, int month, int year, double latitude, double longitude, int seed, int port)
      The constructor of the AppStartInfo class.
      Parameters:
      day - the day of month of the drone's journey
      month - the month of the drone's journey
      year - the year of the drone's journey
      latitude - the latitude the drone starts at
      longitude - the longitude the drone starts at
      seed - a random seed that could be used for reproducibility if any random operations were needed
      port - the port needed to connect to the file server related to this program
